{%- comment -%}
  ===================================================================
  TechAuraz Product Template — 2026 Conversion-Optimized PDP
  ===================================================================
  
  Uses .liquid format instead of .json due to Shopify GitHub sync
  issue with JSON templates (confirmed 2026-03-11).
  
  Section order follows the high-conversion PDP funnel:
  1. Hero (gallery + buy box) — ATF conversion zone
  2. Trust strip — immediate reassurance
  3. Benefits — value proposition
  4. Content box (includes, features, FAQ, usage)
  5. Social proof (testimonials + reviews)
  6. Cross-sell & related products — AOV boosters
  7. Sticky mobile CTA — mobile conversion rescue
  ===================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  ===== BREADCRUMB NAVIGATION =====
  Visible breadcrumbs for UX + Schema.org structured data
{%- endcomment -%}
